file1.highlighted_code: from collections import Counter s = input() counter = Counter(s) fq_odd_cnt = 0 for (_, fq) in counter.items(): if fq % 2 != 0: if fq_odd_cnt == 1: break else: fq_odd_cnt += 1 if fq_odd_cnt <= 1: print("true") else: print("ValueError: Invalid palindrome")
